                    <content>
                        <p>This Order may be cited as the Enterprise Act 2002 (Turnover Test) (Amendment) Order 2018.</p>
                    </content>
                </paragraph>
                <paragraph eId="article-1-2">
                    <num>2</num>
                    <content>
                        <p>This Order comes into force immediately after the commencement of the Enterprise Act 2002 (Share of Supply Test) (Amendment) Order 2018
