            <article eId="article-2">
                <num>2</num>
                <heading>Amendment of the Enterprise Act 2002</heading>
                <paragraph eId="article-2-1">
                    <num>1</num>
                    <content>
                        <p>Section 23 of the Enterprise Act 2002
                            <noteRef href="#f00003" class="footnote" marker="3"/> is amended as follows.
                        </p>
                    </content>
                </paragraph>
                <paragraph eId="article-2-2">
                    <num>2</num>
                    <content>
                        <p>In subsection (1)(b), after “exceeds” insert—</p>
                        <p class="BlockAmendment">
                            <mod>
                                <quotedStructure class="unknown unknown unknown double" startQuote="“" endQuote="”">
                                    <clause eId="d1e131">
                                        <num>i</num>
                                        <content>
                                            <p>£1 million, if in the course of the enterprises ceasing to be distinct, a person or group of persons has brought a relevant enterprise (see section 23A) under the ownership or control of the person or group; or</p>
                                        </content>
                                    </clause>
                                    <clause eId="d1e137">
                                        <num>ii</num>
                                        <content>
                                            <p>£70 million, in any other case.</p>
                                        </content>
                                    </clause>
                                </quotedStructure>
                            </mod>
                            <inline name="AppendText">.</inline>
                        </p>
                    </content>
                </paragraph>
            </article>
            <article eId="article-3">
                <num>3</num>
                <heading>Transitional provision</heading>
                <content>
                    <p>The amendments made by article 
                        <a href="#article-2">2</a> apply only in relation to cases where enterprises cease to be distinct after the commencement of this Order.
                    </p>
                </content>
            </article>
